  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was already-- she-- she didn't join the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when we went to the Negev, we had one-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] one concrete building, [NON-ENGLISH], it has-- that is called house and security building, three barracks out of wood, and a small water tower with perhaps two cubic meter of water.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No water.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the point was 16 kilometers south of [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva. ?] And by having this particular point, the Arabs never really could claim [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva, ?] because [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva ?] suddenly was surrounded by Jewish points.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On one side was [NON-ENGLISH], Nevatim, Revivim, [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We surrounded, actually, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva. ?] We had no street going to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The street ended in [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Beer-Sheva. ?] 15 miles was through the sand-- 15 kilometers was through the sand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And unfortunately, at the same time, the Arab fighting started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the corridor between the northern part of Palestine and the southern part of Palestine is very, very narrow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There is only a strip of land, perhaps 4 kilometer wide, in Jewish hands between the northern and the southern part.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And our-- and, of course, the road goes through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one kibbutz, Negba, is close by actually guarding this narrow point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But we knew if this point is broken, if this strip is broken, the whole southern part of Palestine, the whole Negev, will be isolated.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Strategically, if you look at the old maps, it was a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Nobody could-- nobody with-- with the right mind would believe a country can be held where a strip of land by Jerusalem is only 25 kilometer wide. 40 million Arab-- Arabs were against 800,000--",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "8,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The key's on the side of the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was against the Jews-- 800,000 Jews, 800,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
